OL,7,FFormer patients of the Great North
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital have gathered in
OL,9,FByker, Newcastle, to celebrate the
OL,10,Fachievements of a charity worker who
OL,11,F"helped advance bone marrow
OL,12,Ftransplantation".
OL,14,FGill Wheeldon is the head fundraiser
OL,15,Fat The Bubble Foundation, which
OL,16,Fstarted supporting the hospital's
OL,17,Fchildren's bone marrow transplant unit
OL,18,Fin 1992, and is retiring after 32
OL,19,Fyears in the role.
