OL,7,FGill told ITV News Tyne Tees: "I'm
OL,8,Fvery emotional. I'm surprised and
OL,9,Fseeing parents and previous patients
OL,10,Fand old staff, it's been really
OL,11,Foverwhelming. You know, it was like
OL,12,Fany other ward in the NHS. There was
OL,13,Fnever enough money to go around and I
OL,14,Flooked at the parents and I thought I
OL,15,Fhoped if I was a parent in that
OL,16,Fposition, somebody would help me, so
OL,17,Fthat was how it all started."
