OL,7,FAfter seeing so many former patients
OL,8,Fshe has supported over the years, she
OL,9,Fadded: "It became a mission and I
OL,10,Fwouldn't take no from anybody and if I
OL,11,Fgot a no then I went somewhere else
OL,12,Fand looking back now, and I see these
OL,13,Fchildren here today, I am proud of
OL,14,Fwhat I've achieved."
