OL,7,FProfessor Andrew Cant of Newcastle
OL,8,FUniversity was the consultant who
OL,9,Ffounded the "Bubble Unit". He said the
OL,10,Fcharity work Gill has delivered has
OL,11,Fbeen impactful by supporting children
OL,12,Fand their parents and fundraising for
OL,13,Fspecialist equipment, but he said the
OL,14,Fmedical research she's raised money
OL,15,Ffor and funded has been pioneering.
