OL,7,FHe said: "Without that research, we
OL,8,Fcouldn't improve what we do and even
OL,9,Fbetter than that, the money that the
OL,10,Ffoundation has raised has been
OL,11,Fseedcorn. You fund #100,000 worth of
OL,12,Fresearch, you get results. You can
OL,13,Fthen get a much bigger grant from the
OL,14,Fmedical research. Without the Bubble
OL,15,FFoundation, none of that could have
OL,16,Fbeen possible and we wouldn't have
OL,17,Fadvanced bone marrow transplantation
OL,18,Fin the way that we have."
