OL,7,FFormer patients told ITV News:
OL,8,F"Without her, I wouldn't be living
OL,9,Ftoday and all she's done is really
OL,10,Fwell and really good."
OL,12,FAnother man said: "It means the world
OL,13,Fto me, my family, my children. Without
OL,14,Fthe work that Gill has done, I
OL,15,Fwouldn't be here standing talking to
OL,16,Fyou today."
