OL,7,FOne parent said: "It's the support,
OL,8,Fit's the emotional support as well. We
OL,9,Fwould hear from Gill constantly
OL,10,Fthroughout the years and she's always
OL,11,Fasking for Oscar as well."
OL,13,FGill will retire in Jersey, but said
OL,14,Fshe will always stay in touch with The
OL,15,FBubble Foundation as it continues to
OL,16,Fsupport the hospital.
